metadata.name: Madaari - A Man with the Monkey
metadata.description:
A man with the monkey, 
We call him MADAARI in India, when we were kids, we liked him a lot, the man who show his different tricks and plays with his mate ‘a monkey’, A man who makes a monkey dance, make him cry, jump etc to entertain us.
we enjoyed a lot, but now i think that there is no difference between that monkey and us; like him, we are also controlled by the things, people, desires etc., except one thing, that the monkey doesn't have an another choice to slavery, but we choose to make a slave out of ourselves.

Digital Painting

Edition 1/1

Dimensions: 2160*2160
